short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Look-see helps you find and fix accessibility issues

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Review all elements on a webpage for color contrast issues based on WCAG 2.1 AA and AAA guidelines. Simply click on the button that says "Analyze Page" to review all elements on a webpage for color contrast issues and see a list of all elements that aren't compliant with either WCAG AA or AAA guidelines.
